title: BRIEF-Solucom enters into a partnership with ShiftIN Partners
text:
BRIEF-Solucom enters into a partnership with ShiftIN Partners Sept 22 
Sept 22 Solucom SA : 
* Enters into a partnership with ShiftIN Partners in the GCC 
* Says ShiftIN Partners is a consulting firm headquartered in Abu Dhabi with offices in Dubai and Riyadh, that focuses on strategy execution and innovation management Source text: bit.ly/1j6LYdY Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
